DataSource.RecordSource:
SELECT PO_InvoiceMaster.InvoiceNo, PO_InvoiceMaster.PostDate, PO_InvoiceMaster.ExchangeRate, PO_InvoiceMaster.BLDate, PO_InvoiceMaster.InformDate, PO_InvoiceMaster.DeclarationDate, PO_InvoiceMaster.BLNumber, PO_InvoiceMaster.TaxInformNumber, PO_InvoiceMaster.TaxDeclarationNumber, PO_InvoiceMaster.TotalInlandAmount, PO_InvoiceMaster.TotalCIPAmount, PO_InvoiceMaster.TotalCIFAmount, PO_InvoiceMaster.TotalImportTax, PO_InvoiceMaster.TotalBeforeVATAmount, PO_InvoiceMaster.TotalVATAmount, MST_Party.Code + ' (' + MST_Party.Name + ')' as PartyCodeName, MST_DeliveryTerm.Code AS DeliveryTermCode, MST_Currency.Code AS CurrencyCode, MST_Carrier.Code AS CarrierCode, MST_PaymentTerm.Code AS PaymentTermCode, PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.Code AS PONo, PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.Line as POLine, ITM_Product.Code as PartNumber, ITM_Product.Revision as PartModel, ITM_Product.Description as PartName, ITM_Product.OtherInfo1 as CustomsCode, ITM_Product.PartNameVN, ITM_Product.TaxCode, PO_DeliverySchedule.DeliveryLine, MST_UnitOfMeasure.Code AS UMCode, PO_InvoiceDetail.InvoiceLine, PO_InvoiceDetail.InvoiceQuantity, PO_InvoiceDetail.UnitPrice, PO_InvoiceDetail.VAT, PO_InvoiceDetail.VATAmount, PO_InvoiceDetail.ImportTax, PO_InvoiceDetail.ImportTaxAmount, PO_InvoiceDetail.Inland, PO_InvoiceDetail.BeforeVATAmount, PO_InvoiceDetail.CIFAmount, PO_InvoiceDetail.CIPAmount, PO_InvoiceDetail.Note
FROM PO_InvoiceMaster INNER JOIN PO_InvoiceDetail ON PO_InvoiceDetail.InvoiceMasterID = PO_InvoiceMaster.InvoiceMasterID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderMaster ON PO_InvoiceDetail.PurchaseOrderMasterID = PO_PurchaseOrderMaster.PurchaseOrderMasterID INNER JOIN ITM_Product ON PO_InvoiceDetail.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID INNER JOIN MST_Currency ON PO_InvoiceMaster.CurrencyID = MST_Currency.CurrencyID INNER JOIN PO_PurchaseOrderDetail ON PO_InvoiceDetail.PurchaseOrderDetailID = PO_PurchaseOrderDetail.PurchaseOrderDetailID INNER JOIN MST_Party ON PO_InvoiceMaster.PartyID = MST_Party.PartyID LEFT JOIN MST_Carrier ON PO_InvoiceMaster.CarrierID = MST_Carrier.CarrierID LEFT JOIN MST_PaymentTerm ON PO_InvoiceMaster.PaymentTermID = MST_PaymentTerm.PaymentTermID LEFT JOIN MST_DeliveryTerm ON PO_InvoiceMaster.DeliveryTermID = MST_DeliveryTerm.DeliveryTermID LEFT JOIN PO_DeliverySchedule ON PO_InvoiceDetail.DeliveryScheduleID = PO_DeliverySchedule.DeliveryScheduleID LEFT JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure ON PO_InvoiceDetail.InvoiceUMID = MST_UnitOfMeasure.UnitOfMeasureID
WHERE PO_InvoiceMaster.InvoiceMasterID = 6
ORDER BY PO_InvoiceDetail.InvoiceLine ASC
